snippet.title: Black Mesa Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Black Mesa Trailer is good to go and up for viewing!

You can download the high resolution version straight off of Monkey-Junkie's website: Monkeyjunkie.co.uk/bms

We hope this gives you a small taste of what the game will be like! Thanks to the entire team for their effort!

Filmed and edited by Monkey-Junkie
Soundtrack by Joel Nielson
